    <title>Hexo[Next] @ Set transparency and margins</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/09/01/2020-09-01-Hexo-Next-Set-transparency-and-margins/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/09/01/2020-09-01-Hexo-Next-Set-transparency-and-margins/</id>
    <published>2020-08-31T22:53:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-08-31T23:02:25.117Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Go to the custom style file:</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ./site_folder/source/_data/styles.styl | vi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Add the code as below:</p><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;1_The menu bar tranparency</span><br><span class="line">.header-inner &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); &#x2F;&#x2F;from 0-1</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;2_Avatar info bar</span><br><span class="line">.sidebar &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  opacity: 0.85;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;3_local-search box</span><br><span class="line">.popup &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  opacity: 0.9;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;4_post tranparency and middle body tranparency</span><br><span class="line">.main-inner &#123; </span><br><span class="line">    margin-top: 20px;  &#x2F;&#x2F;Margin from the top of the page</span><br><span class="line">    padding: 20px 40px 20px 40px; &#x2F;&#x2F; page margin for up,right,down,and left.</span><br><span class="line">    background: none; &#x2F;&#x2F;The page margin color, #fff [white] is default. &#x2F;&#x2F;&quot;none&quot; is transparent</span><br><span class="line">    opacity: 0.90;     </span><br><span class="line">    min-height: 500px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>You can now customize all the transparency of your site and margins.</p><p>Good luck！</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Go to the custom style file:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight shell&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;cd ./site_folder/source/_data/styles.styl | vi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;



