    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>To make the page look more comfortable,  we need further add the rounded corners for page block.</p><p>First, should know your Next_theme type, here we use  <code>Gemini</code> </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ./site_floder/themes/next/source/css/_variables/Gemini.styl |vi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>add the follow code should be OK:</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">$border-radius-inner</span>              <span class="string">=</span> <span class="string">20px</span> <span class="string">//</span> <span class="string">for</span> <span class="string">menu</span> <span class="string">bar</span> <span class="string">and</span> <span class="string">main</span> <span class="string">text</span> <span class="string">block</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">$border-radius</span>                    <span class="string">=</span> <span class="string">20px</span> <span class="string">//</span> <span class="string">only</span> <span class="string">for</span> <span class="string">personal</span> <span class="string">info</span> <span class="string">sidebar</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>The rendering is as follows: </p><a id="more"></a><img src="/images/image-20200831234709921.png" alt="image-20200831234709921" style="zoom: 67%;" />]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;To make the page look more comfortable,  we need further add the rounded corners for page block.&lt;/p&gt;
